<DocsPageTitle Path="Extensions/ListView">
    Blazorise ListView component
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageLead>
    The <Code>ListView</Code> component renders a scrollable list of items with selection and templating support.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageParagraph>
