<DocsPageParagraph>
    The <Code>ListView</Code> component uses <Code>ListGroup</Code> under the hood, so you can also use the underlying <Code>ListGroup</Code> APIs when needed.
</DocsPageParagraph>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    To use the <Code>ListView</Code> component, install the <Code>Blazorise.Components</Code> package first.
</DocsPageParagraph>

